Class AbstractMultiQuantifierEliminator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sri.ai.grinder.core.solver.AbstractMultiQuantifierEliminator

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractIterativeMultiQuantifierEliminator, AbstractSGVET, DefaultMultiQuantifierEliminator, SamplingIfNeededMultiQuantifierEliminator

    public abstract class AbstractMultiQuantifierEliminator
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultiQuantifierEliminator
    A MultiQuantifierEliminator implementing interruption and debugging mechanisms.

    Extensions to this class must routinely invoke checkInterrupted() during its operation so as to allow interruption ordered by client code.

    braz
